"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/788445","Ministry of Defence","false","2017-11-21","<p>Recording accountancy qualifications is not mandated, so data is only that which is recorded on the Ministry of Defence Human Resources system.</p><p> </p><p>The information requested, as at 30 June 2017, is given below:</p><p> </p><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>Single Service</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>Navy</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>Navy</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>Air</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Total Number Qualified Accountants</p></td><td><p>20</p></td><td><p>20</p></td><td><p>15</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Total Number Under Training</p></td><td><p>~</p></td><td><p>~</p></td><td><p>5</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Do not have a professional accountancy qualification</p></td><td><p>115</p></td><td><p>320</p></td><td><p>145</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table><tbody><tr><td colspan="7"><p>In line with Defence Statistics policy, all figures have been rounded to the nearest 5. ~ represents less than 5.</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan="7"><p> </p></td></tr><tr><td colspan="5"><p>Number of staff is headcount.</p></td></tr></tbody></table>","Bournemouth East","Mr Tobias Ellwood",,"2017-11-21T14:41:13.943Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/788445/answer","Biography information for Mr Tobias Ellwood","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/788445/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/788445/answer",,,,,,,,"11","Defence","Defence","2017-11-13","Armed Forces","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Defence, how many finance staff within (a) Navy, (b) Army and (c) Air Command (i) have (ii) are working towards and (iii) do not have a professional accountancy qualification.","false","Biography information for Mr Kevan Jones","North Durham","Mr Kevan Jones","112469"
